<img style="float:left" src="/upload/thumb150_blueprint.jpg"> <center><p style="font-size: 14px;"><ul style="font-size: 14px;">
Our 1st Edition Pathtags went on sale in in August, 2013, and sold out in March, 2014 (the last few packs were discounted). We also used the Pathtags fundraiser program with an initial run of 400. The site Admins did place a refill order, so 500 were originally made. These tags are now very rare! If you find one, consider yourself very lucky! They have technically never been retired, but it's very unlikely we will ever order more, in favor of commisioning a 3rd Edition OCNA Pathtag in the future. </p> </center>

